ificationHeading\">Alerts In Effect</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Dismiss\" class=\"AlertsNotification__DismissButton\" type=\"button\">\nDismiss\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#close\"></use>\n</svg>\n</button>\n<span class=\"hr clearfix\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Body\" id=\"AlertsNotificationBody\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLinkContainer\">\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#add\"></use>\n</svg>\n<a class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLink\" href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/conditions.htm\" id=\"AlertsNotificationMoreLink\" tabindex=\"-1\">\nmore information on current conditions...\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"MainContent\" id=\"main\" role=\"main\">\n\n<div aria-labelledby=\"modal-contact-us-label\" class=\"modal fade\" id=\"modal-contact-us\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h4 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"modal-contact-us-label\">Contact Us</h4>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"adminTools\"></div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"ContentHeader text-content-size\">\n<h1 class=\"page-title\">Kids &amp; Youth</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Layout\" id=\"cs_control_2\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"CS_Layout_Table\" id=\"cs_idLayout2\" summary=\"\" width=\"100%\"><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x1x1\" width=\"100%\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6813946\">\n<div class=\"Component ListingGrid -large\">\n<div class=\"ListingGrid-header\">\n<h2 class=\"Tag\">Programs and Activities</h2>\n</div>\n<ul class=\"row\">\n<li class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing\">\n<a class=\"ActivityListing-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/kidsyouth/junior-ranger.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send','event','Graphic Grid',document.location.href,'/grca/learn/kidsyouth/junior-ranger.htm',1,true)\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"A ranger helps a group of four kids with there Junior Ranger book.\" class=\"ActivityListing-image\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/F7DC41A0-9F65-BD43-B9E46FCDD657CECE.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/F7DC41A0-9F65-BD43-B9E46FCDD657CECE.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\"/>\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-titleContainer\">\n<span class=\"ActivityListing-subtitle\">During Your Visit</span>\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-title\">\nBecome a Junior Ranger\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#navigate_next\"></use>\n</svg>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"ActivityListing-description\">How to become a Junior Ranger during your visit.</p>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing\">\n<a class=\"ActivityListing-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/kidsyouth/teens.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send','event','Graphic Grid',document.location.href,'/grca/learn/kidsyouth/teens.htm',1,true)\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"Three students make inquisitive faces at the camera while hiking on a red dusty trail.\" class=\"ActivityListing-image\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/EE4D25D6-CB8E-10C5-C81C3A0D5CDED7E8.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/EE4D25D6-CB8E-10C5-C81C3A0D5CDED7E8.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\"/>\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-titleContainer\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-title\">\nYouth and Teens\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#navigate_next\"></use>\n</svg>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"ActivityListing-description\">Are you a teenager looking for a camp or work experience in the outdoors? The National Park Service has engaging and educational programs.</p>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing\">\n<a class=\"ActivityListing-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/education/index.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send','event','Graphic Grid',document.location.href,'/grca/learn/education/index.htm',1,true)\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"A group of kids, a couple teachers, and a couple of park rangers with the canyon in the background.\" class=\"ActivityListing-image\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/D72A5D05-1DD8-B71B-0B2126AC1EF4EF4A.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/D72A5D05-1DD8-B71B-0B2126AC1EF4EF4A.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\"/>\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-titleContainer\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-title\">\nEducational Programs\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#navigate_next\"></use>\n</svg>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"ActivityListing-description\">Teachers and students: learn throughout the school year.</p>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing\">\n<a class=\"ActivityListing-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/education/student-report-information.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send','event','Graphic Grid',document.location.href,'/grca/learn/education/student-report-information.htm',1,true)\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"Tree with brown bark and green needles in the foreground, with an view of the Grand Canyon behind.\" class=\"ActivityListing-image\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/1EEE8CBA-FFA1-747B-EAA5225A114C5F89.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/1EEE8CBA-FFA1-747B-EAA5225A114C5F89.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\"/>\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-titleContainer\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-title\">\nStudent Report Information\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#navigate_next\"></use>\n</svg>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"ActivityListing-description\">Resources are available for classroom and home learning; for teachers or students! Search by subject matter to learn more. </p>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing\">\n<a class=\"ActivityListing-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/management/statistics.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send','event','Graphic Grid',document.location.href,'/grca/learn/management/statistics.htm',1,true)\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"Jagged limestone pillars frame sunset-lit peaks in a vast canyon.\" class=\"ActivityListing-image\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/48C30444-DAFA-948B-61252F7BF069E069.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/48C30444-DAFA-948B-61252F7BF069E069.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\"/>\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-titleContainer\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-title\">\nPark Overview\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#navigate_next\"></use>\n</svg>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"ActivityListing-description\">Fun facts about the geology, geography, climate, history, and the park's natural and cultural resources.</p>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing\">\n<a class=\"ActivityListing-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/kidsyouth/sesame-street-grca.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send','event','Graphic Grid',document.location.href,'/grca/learn/kidsyouth/sesame-street-grca.htm',1,true)\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"Muppets Elmo and Murray along with Park Ranger Amala From Grand Canyon.\" class=\"ActivityListing-image\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/D4300C52-1DD8-B71B-0B659870EF32C4FD.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/D4300C52-1DD8-B71B-0B659870EF32C4FD.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\"/>\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-titleContainer\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-title\">\nSesame Street Explores National Parks\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#navigate_next\"></use>\n</svg>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"ActivityListing-description\">Elmo and Murray Discover the wonders of Grand Canyon and Gateway with the help of Ranger Amala.</p>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x2x1\" width=\"100%\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"/commonspot/images/clear.gif\" style=\"display:block;\" width=\"1\"/></td></tr><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x3x1\" width=\"100%\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"/commonspot/images/clear.gif\" style=\"display:block;\" width=\"1\"/></td></tr>\n</table></div>\n</div><!-- col-sm-12 -->\n</div><!-- row -->\n</div><!-- ColumnMain col-sm-